Type of Feat: Class
The stormsinger can use her bardic music ability to create various storm-related effects in addition to the normal uses of bardic music.
A stormsinger of 1st level or higher with 9 or more ranks in Perform can use bardic music to generate a gust of wind, as the spell of the same name. Her caster level is equal to her ranks in Perform, with a maximum caster level of 30th.
Use: Selected.